Type: Package
Title: Boundary Corrected Polynomial Adaptive Kernel Conditional Density Estimation
Version: 1.50
Date: 2026-03-09
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = c("Jeffrey", "S."), family = "Racine",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "racinej@mcmaster.ca")
 )
Description: Boundary-corrected polynomial adaptive kernel conditional density
    estimation for bounded or partially bounded responses. The package provides
    likelihood and least-squares cross-validation, optional sub-sampled
    bandwidth selection for large samples, automatic polynomial-order
    selection, and methods for plotting, prediction, and summary.
